						<summary>

						<p>This is a verse in praise of the chief Vīramāgadan Rājarājadēvan Ponparappināṉ Magadaipperumāḷ. It also mentions a fight between the chief Vāṇaṉ Vaḍivēlāṉ and the Pāṇḍya king (<hi rend="italic">Teṉṉavar-kōṉ</hi>)</p>						

