<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> viramākataṉ Irā[<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>*]rā[<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>*]tevaṉ poṉparappiṉāṉ ma
<lb n="2" break="no"/>kataipperumāḷ makataipperuveḷḷam vārātākiṉ
<lb n="3"/>peruveḷḷap peruñcāvi pokātākil Iṭṭa tiṭṭukku O
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṉṟukkoṟarai kuṭukkakaṭavatu—iḻaittapaṭi yituvo veṅ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>kaṇāveṉṟeṉṟaḻaitta vaḻukuraleyāṉ taḻaitta kuṭaimaṉ
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṉavar koṉ vāṇaṉ vaṭivelān toṟṟuṭainta teṉṉa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>varkoṉ pecuṉ ticai <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> 
</p>

